		(uuid "8245e9b1-8523-43b3-953e-f86d2d149c31")
	)
	(text "Button grids take up:\n- Serial in\n- Serial out\n- Serial clock\n- Interrupts 0 and 1 (Per grid, 16 pins). Alternatively, poll.\n- Chip select (Per grid, 8 pins)\n- RGB LED driver\n\nTotal: 28 pins\n\nRP2354B has 48 GPIOs, RP2354A 30 GPIOs"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at -110.744 119.634 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "86cbb480-25dc-4941-bbf9-df08fdc0a800")
	)
	(text "Remaining IO requirements:\n- MIDI in (1 pin)\n- MIDI out (1 pin)\n- Clock inputs (8 pins)\n- Trig outputs (8 pins)\n- i2c clock & data\n\nTotal: 20 pins\n\nGrand total: 48 pins!"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at -110.49 143.002 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "894868fd-4b14-4fd8-8e2a-f90e537917b2")
	)
